---
title: Easy Creamy Pork Risotto with Lemon & Parmesan
description: If you haven't tried pork in a risotto before, well, what can we say – you're missing out! Give it a go with this easy baked risotto,
also studded with rounds of carrot, gooey Parmesan and silky baby spinach.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-creamy-pork-risotto-cbb7b8d4.jpg
